{"tid":1952133,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"防暴警員太子站附近舉藍旗警告市民勿再聚集 否則會以武力驅散","createTime":"2020-03-31T12:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T12:07:27.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"150fcf8c90a0dcb1a874ae13d7fc7271f51578d3","tid":1952133,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:03:27.000Z","msg":"防暴警員太子站附近舉藍旗警告市民勿再聚集<br />\n31.03.2020 19:58<br />\n<br />\n港鐵太子站831事件發生七個月，傍晚後陸續有市民到旺角警署對出太子站B1出入口外獻白花，之後離開。有部分穿黑衣的人，停在太子站外叫口號，大批防暴警員到太子站附近增援，並舉藍旗警告市民不要再聚集，否則會以武力驅散。<br />\n<br />\n由於警方封鎖太子站外範圍，多名油尖旺區議員在封鎖線外默站，並放置紙箱讓市民放下鮮花。有區議員指，希望協助市民進行相關行動，會與其他區議員保持適當距離，不擔心違反不能多於4人聚集的法例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1277874&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1277874%26csid%3D261_341&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhpE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=69dba7a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1277874&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"1e8e1dee8cf64f1a035b482c9edcfd7f033e3a78","tid":1952133,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:04:09.000Z","msg":"行路都犯法"},{"pid":"2330d9b80a44a2881212c80c406a0102f2754dbe","tid":1952133,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}